    public class JdbcConnectionPoolStats
extends AbstractCarinaMbean
implements JdbcConnectionPoolStatsMBean
    An implementation of JdbcConnectionPoolStatsMBean exposing connection pool statistics for JDBC data sources, and extending AbstractCarinaMbean in order to enjoy its standard N4 MBean lifecycle management
